
- Update the Raspian OS
  sudo apt-get update
  sudo apt-get upgrade
  
- Turn off Sleep
  sudo nano ~/.config/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart
  Using directional keys move the cursor down the end of the file
  
  + Add the following lines
  @xset s 0 0
  @xset s noblank
  @xset s noexpose
  @xset dpms 0 0 0
  
  + Save the changes
  Ctrl + X 
  Hit 'y' and then enter
  
  sudo reboot

- Disable Mouse Cursor
  sudo apt-get install unclutter
  unclutter -display :0 -noevents -grab
  
